### 2.8 Checklist for Compact Reports

Before finalizing, ask:
- [ ] Can I read this in 3 minutes?
- [ ] Is every sentence necessary?
- [ ] Can any paragraph become a bullet list?
- [ ] Can any list become a table?
- [ ] Are there redundant explanations?
- [ ] Did I use visual shortcuts (â†’, â‘ â‘¡â‘¢, tables)?
- [ ] Is the problem â†’ solution â†’ impact flow clear?
- [ ] Would an executive understand this at a glance?

